26// Opus decoder API for use as a template parameter to
27// CreateAudioDecoderFactory<...>().
28struct RTC_EXPORT AudioDecoderMultiChannelOpus {
29 using Config = AudioDecoderMultiChannelOpusConfig;
30 static absl::optional<AudioDecoderMultiChannelOpusConfig> SdpToConfig(
31 const SdpAudioFormat& audio_format);
32 static void AppendSupportedDecoders(std::vector<AudioCodecSpec>* specs);
33 static std::unique_ptr<AudioDecoder> MakeAudioDecoder(
34 AudioDecoderMultiChannelOpusConfig config,
35 absl::optional<AudioCodecPairId> codec_pair_id = absl::nullopt);
36};
